    "units" => 3, 
    "title" => "Introduction to Principles of Professional Communication", 
    "description" => "This course introduces students to key principles and rhetorical strategies of writing texts in non-academic settings. Although the course may address issues of oral communication, the primary focus will be on learning and practicing strategies to generate written documents in a business context." 
