    "units" => 4, 
    "title" => "International Rural Development Policy", 
    "description" => "Comparative analysis of policy systems governing natural resource development in the rural Third World. Emphasis on organization and function of agricultural and mineral development, with particular consideration of rural hunger, resource availability, technology, and patterns of international aid." 
