    "description" => "For Math/Applied math majors. Supervised experience relevant to specific aspects of their mathmatical emphasis of study in off-campus organizations. Regular individual meetings with faculty sponsor and written reports required. Units will be awarded on the basis of three hours/week/unit." 
  }, 
