    "units" => 3, 
    "title" => "Seq: Methods and Applications", 
    "description" => "A graduate seminar class in which a group of students will closely examine recent computational methods in high-throughput sequencing followed by directly examining interesting biological applications thereof. Also listed as Mathematics C243." 
  }, 
