    "title" => "Reproductive and Perinatal Epidemiology", 
    "description" => "Research methods and issues in perinatal and reproductive epidemiology with emphasis on methods of study. Specific adverse reproductive outcomes, risk factors, and prevalence will be discussed. Will include critiques of published studies and techniques of proposal writing." 
  }, 
  { 
